        public boolean isExtensionEnabled(String extensionName)
        Tells whether or not an Extension with the given extensionName is enabled.
        Parameters:
        extensionName - the name of the extension
        Returns:
        true if the extension is enabled, false otherwise.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the extensionName is null.
        See Also:
